content:
You're welcome! It's my pleasure to help you discover new books and authors. I'm always excited to hear about readers' experiences with the books I recommend, so please do come back and share your thoughts on "The Alice Network" and "The Women in the Castle". I'd love to discuss them with you!

In the meantime, happy reading! I hope you enjoy your journey through the world of historical fiction and WWII stories. If you have any more questions or need further recommendations, don't hesitate to ask.

Remember, I'm always here to help you find your next great read!
